        <text>
            <body>
                <p>Ego <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324645" xml:id="d1e169812" corresp="Étienne II, évêque d'Autun (1171-1189)">Stephanus, Dei gratia
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#319548" xml:id="d1e169814" corresp="Autun (Saône-et-Loire, Autun)">Eduensis</placeName>
                        episcopus</persName>, notum fieri volo presentibus et futuris quod <persName key="d1e30560" xml:id="d1e169818">Osmundus</persName> et <persName key="d1e30566" xml:id="d1e169821">Odo</persName> et <persName key="d1e30572" xml:id="d1e169824">Valdricus filii <persName key="d1e30578" xml:id="d1e169826">Bartholomei de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324475" xml:id="d1e169828" corresp="Marmagne (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Marmania</placeName>
                        </persName>
                    </persName>, laudantibus <persName key="d1e30585" xml:id="d1e169831">matre sua
                        Helysabeth</persName> et <persName key="d1e30591" xml:id="d1e169835">sororibus suis Petronilla</persName> et <persName key="d1e30597" xml:id="d1e169838">Adelina</persName>, pacem fecerunt cum monachis <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e169841" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName> de omnibus
                    querelis quas tam ipsi quam pater eorum habuerant adversus eosdem
                        mona<supplied>chos</supplied> hoc modo. Guirpiverunt omnem calumpniam quam
                    eisdem monachis de decimis suis faciebant ita ut nunquam amplius ab eis in
                    territorio <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324450" xml:id="d1e169849" corresp="Fain-lès-Montbard (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Fanii</placeName>
                    decimas exigant. Laudaverunt quoque monachis <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325163" xml:id="d1e169853" corresp="ortum suum subtus abbatiam">ortum suum subtus abbatiam</placeName> et pratum sub
                        <persName key="d1e30603" xml:id="d1e169856">chimino Fanii ubi Miles
                        jacet</persName> et lescheriam desuper <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324450" xml:id="d1e169859" corresp="Fain-lès-Montbard (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Fanium</placeName> et salceium quod habebant supra eamdem
                    lescheriam et omnes vineas quas monachi tenebant in territorio <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324450" xml:id="d1e169862" corresp="Fain-lès-Montbard (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Fanii</placeName>, vineam scilicet
                        <persName key="d1e30609" xml:id="d1e169865">Rainaldi
                            <addName>Embrasati</addName>
                    </persName>, vineam <persName key="d1e30615" xml:id="d1e169870">Warnerii <addName>
                            <foreign>Vitecoth</foreign>
                        </addName>
                    </persName>, vineam <persName key="d1e30622" xml:id="d1e169877">Odonis <addName>
                            <foreign>Brandun</foreign>
                        </addName>
                    </persName> et terram juxta eamdem vineam, quicquid scilicet ibi in dominio
                    habebant et partem <persName key="d1e30628" xml:id="d1e169883">Odonis <addName>
                            <foreign>Brandun</foreign>
                        </addName>
                    </persName> quando eam conquirere poterunt et terram <persName key="d1e30634" xml:id="d1e169889">Warnerii <addName>
                            <foreign>Vitecoth</foreign>
                        </addName>
                    </persName> quam habebat ad censum pro duobus nummis in costa <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324489" xml:id="d1e169895" corresp="Morville (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Morville</placeName>. Quod autem de
                    his omnibus predicte ecclesie semper fideles existerent et quod adversus omnes
                    qui de his calumpniam moverent eis semper legitimam garentiam portarent <hi rend="background(green)">super veram crucem Domini ante <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324453" xml:id="d1e169900" corresp="Fontenay (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">altare Fonteneti</placeName>
                        juraverunt</hi>. <persName key="d1e30640" xml:id="d1e169904">Stephanum
                        quoque cognatum suum</persName> de his omnibus responsorem dederunt. Pro his
                    autem omnibus <num>ccc</num>
                    <hi rend="superscript">os</hi> solidos de intragio dederunt eis monachi et
                    semper annuatim dabunt eis <num>xx</num> solidos census in martio et matri eorum
                    unum sextarium frumenti et unum trimensis tantum in vita sua. Unde testes sunt
                        <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324625" xml:id="d1e169916" corresp="Hugo archipresbiter Pulleniaci">Hugo archipresbiter
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324344" xml:id="d1e169918" corresp="Pouillenay (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Puilleniaci</placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324623" xml:id="d1e169921" corresp="Eudes, archiprêtre de Touillon (1173-1200)">Odo
                        archipresbiter <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324370" xml:id="d1e169923" corresp="Touillon (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Tullionis</placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e30646" xml:id="d1e169926">Humbertus capellanus de
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324350" xml:id="d1e169928" corresp="Ravières (Yonne, Tonnerrois)">Raveriis</placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e30652" xml:id="d1e169932">Iterius
                            <addName>Buro</addName>
                    </persName> et <persName key="d1e30659" xml:id="d1e169937">Villelmus dominus de
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324350" xml:id="d1e169939" corresp="Ravières (Yonne, Tonnerrois)">Raveriis</placeName>
                    </persName>
                    <witDetail wit="#B">"Iterius… Raverius" écrit en marge</witDetail>, <persName key="d1e30665" xml:id="d1e169944">Bernardus <addName>Brabentio</addName>
                    </persName> et <persName key="d1e30671" xml:id="d1e169949">Oliverius filius
                            <persName key="d1e30677" xml:id="d1e169951">Brutini</persName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e30683" xml:id="d1e169954">Robertus filius
                            <persName key="d1e30689" xml:id="d1e169956">majoris de
                            Tullione</persName>
                    </persName> et <persName key="d1e30696" xml:id="d1e169960">Johannes frater
                        ejus</persName>, <persName key="d1e30702" xml:id="d1e169963">Durannus major
                        Fanii</persName> et <persName key="d1e30708" xml:id="d1e169966">
                        <foreign>Hugonez</foreign> poslerius de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324475" xml:id="d1e169973" corresp="Marmagne (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Marmania</placeName>
                    </persName>.</p>
                <p>De laude matris eorum atque sororum testes sunt <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324623" xml:id="d1e169978" corresp="Eudes, archiprêtre de Touillon (1173-1200)">Odo archipresbiter</persName> et <persName key="d1e30714" xml:id="d1e169981">Humbertus capellanus de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324350" xml:id="d1e169983" corresp="Ravières (Yonne, Tonnerrois)">Raveriis</placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e30720" xml:id="d1e169986">Willermus dominus de
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324350" xml:id="d1e169988" corresp="Ravières (Yonne, Tonnerrois)">Raveriis</placeName>
                    </persName> et <persName key="d1e30726" xml:id="d1e169991">Stephanus gener
                        ejus</persName>, <persName key="d1e30733" xml:id="d1e169994">Osmundus de
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324341" xml:id="d1e169996" corresp="Planay (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Plaaneto</placeName>
                    </persName> et <persName key="d1e30739" xml:id="d1e170000">Rainaldus major
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324370" xml:id="d1e170002" corresp="Touillon (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Tulionis</placeName>
                    </persName> cum <persName key="d1e30745" xml:id="d1e170005">Johanne filio
                        suo</persName>.</p>
                <p>Hec igitur omnia se fecisse, dedisse et laudasse coram me recognoverunt et ut
                    sigillo meo confirmarem postulaverunt. Proinde ut ista in posterum stabili
                    firmitate serventur cartam presentem sigilli mei munimine firmo et omnes qui de
                    hiis ecclesiam <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e170010" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName> in aliquo vexare aut dampnum aliquod inferre aussi
                    fuerint donec resipiscant anathemate dampno. </p>
